column7: For transactions conducted in SAP Ariba, invoices shall be submitted directly through Ariba. For invoices paid by ACH or by check, unless stated otherwise, invoices shall be electronically submitted by email to accountspayable@examplecity1.
They prepaid for 100 signs in 2021. As of Dec 15th, 2021 66 out of 100 signs in the 2021 contract had been sent out.
As of Jun 24, 2022, 32 more packets of the 2021 budget had gone out, leaving 2 more remaining from the 2021 contract.
In final 2022 invoice, charged 25 packets instead of 27 because of the 2 remaining prepaid packets from 2021..
Mistake in math on contract. Looks like the Welcome packets and cards ($110) were not included in the total even though they are shown in the budget.
